###  http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8#滑移—拉裂
<http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8#滑移—拉裂> rdf:type owl:Class ;
                                                                               rdfs:subClassOf :e.滑动机理 .


###  http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8#蠕滑—拉裂
<http://www.semanticweb.org/94180/ontologies/2023/3/untitled-ontology-8#蠕滑—拉裂> rdf:type owl:Class ;
